Amazon Sales Dashboard 2011-2014
Project Overview

This project is an interactive Amazon Sales Dashboard created using Microsoft Excel and Power Pivot to analyze sales performance, profitability, customer activity, and business growth trends from 2011–2014.

The dashboard transforms raw sales data into meaningful business insights using KPI reporting, interactive filters, and data visualization techniques.

Dashboard Insights
Total Sales reached 12.6M, showing strong overall business performance.
Total Profit generated was 1.47M, indicating healthy profitability.
Total Orders recorded were 5.1K, reflecting consistent customer purchasing activity.
Profit Margin stood at 11.6%, highlighting stable operational efficiency.
Business Insights
Central region generated the highest sales among all regions.
Technology category contributed the highest revenue share.
Sales increased consistently from 2011 to 2014, showing positive business growth trends.
